      <p class="svc-intro__body" style="font-weight:600; color:var(--hmc-verdigris);">Highly recommended for best results - from $1,500 + GST per month</p>
      <p class="svc-intro__body">For ambitious business owners ready to fix reactive marketing for good. You&rsquo;ve built something real. But the sales pipeline is unpredictable, you&rsquo;re working harder than you should be, and &ldquo;doing more marketing&rdquo; isn&rsquo;t a strategy.</p>
      <p class="svc-intro__body">Marketing moves fast. New platforms, shifting algorithms, emerging tools. Standing out and keeping up feels hard. Kristy stays across the latest strategies, tools, and market shifts so you don&rsquo;t have to. What&rsquo;s working right now gets built into your plan from the start. We build the marketing foundations, create the strategy, set the systems, and work with you and your team to implement it week after week, until consistency becomes your competitive advantage.</p>
      <a href="https://calendly.com/huntermarketingco/free-15-min-marketing-consultation-call" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn--primary btn--mustard" style="margin-top:32px;display:inline-block;">Book a discovery call &rarr;</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ PARALLAX IMAGE ============ -->
<div class="svc-parallax" role="img" aria-label="Kristy Hunter leading a marketing strategy session with a client team around a boardroom table in Brisbane"></div>

